Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/maxedoutstudio/othello_ai
# Conflicts: # src/Board.java # src/Game.java # src/HumanPlayer.java # src/Player.java # src/Sample/GameDriver.java # src/Sample/GameMoves.java # src/Sample/GameOthello.java # src/Sample/GamePanel.java # src/Sample/GameSquare.java # src/Sample/GameState.java

Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/maxedoutstudio/othello_ai
# Conflicts: # src/Board.java # src/Game.java # src/HumanPlayer.java # src/Player.java # src/Sample/GameDriver.java # src/Sample/GameMoves.java # src/Sample/GameOthello.java # src/Sample/GamePanel.java # src/Sample/GameSquare.java # src/Sample/GameState.java
Added loop logic, victory conditions to Game class. Changed up color stuff in board.
Changed stuff in Player, Game. PvP now functional.
Fixed issue where placing at 7th row would throw Index out of bounds exception. Removed class files.
Started changes in MinMax, started changing algorithm to do DFS alpha-beta pruning.
Fixed up min-max to use proper alpha beta algorithm. To test.
Basic greedy ai working. Im too bad to win against it.
Multiple AIs implemented. Work to be done on heuristics.
Fixed index out of bounds error for maksym heuristic #2.
Added support for turn timers (oh god why, this took soo long. Why is there no simpelr way to do this!>!)
Fixed issue where skipping turns would no longer work. Skipping a turn for HumanPlayerConsole is now " " (space)
